{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDk5NTQ2MTU0", "number": 8002, "title": "properly resolve sourcerefs for bytecode contexts", "bodyText": "Intent\nWhen R byte-compiles a function, the context that is placed on the stack is slightly different in form. In particular, the srcref field associated with the context is replaced with an <in-bc-interp> marker, and the \"true\" source references need to be resolved separately.\nApproach\nDetect byte-code contexts, and resolve their contexts by finding the associated R system call + function on the stack, and retrieve the source reference from the matching call object.\nQA Notes\nTest via notes in #6922, but also worth running the \"regular\" debugger test suite to ensure this doesn't regress elsewhere.\nCloses #6922.", "createdAt": "2020-10-07T22:15:24Z", "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/pull/8002", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "18719b24084158305e21c01a5fcc2096eee395c6"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-10-09T19:28:41Z", "author": {"login": "kevinushey"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 10, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdQV4UsgFqTUwNDM0MTcwMg==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdQ6o1PgFqTUwNTkwODcyOA==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTA0MzQxNzAy", "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/pull/8002#pullrequestreview-504341702", "createdAt": "2020-10-07T23:46:37Z", "commit": {"oid": "ac1b6575cdd71e4c6e98a8feaebf632669ef5daf"}, "state": "COMMENTED", "comments": {"totalCount": 3, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0xMC0wN1QyMzo0NjozOFrOHeJU3Q==", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpK0MjAyMC0xMC0wN1QyMzo0OToxM1rOHeJYLw==", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMTM3MjEyNQ==", "bodyText": "nit: exact = TRUE?", "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/pull/8002#discussion_r501372125", "createdAt": "2020-10-07T23:46:38Z", "author": {"login": "jmcphers"}, "path": "src/cpp/session/modules/SessionEnvironment.R", "diffHunk": "@@ -735,3 +735,18 @@\n    .Call(\"rs_hasAltrep\", var, PACKAGE = \"(embedding)\")\n })\n \n+.rs.addFunction(\"resolveContextSourceRefs\", function(info)\n+{\n+   calls <- sys.calls()\n+   \n+   for (i in seq_along(calls))\n+   {\n+      fn <- sys.function(i)\n+      if (identical(fn, info$callfun))\n+         return(attr(calls[[i]], \"srcref\"))", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "ac1b6575cdd71e4c6e98a8feaebf632669ef5daf"}, "originalPosition": 12}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMTM3Mjc1Ng==", "bodyText": "It doesn't look like the the function actually uses most of these values -- do we need them all?", "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/pull/8002#discussion_r501372756", "createdAt": "2020-10-07T23:48:43Z", "author": {"login": "jmcphers"}, "path": "src/cpp/r/RCntxt.cpp", "diffHunk": "@@ -81,6 +81,41 @@ bool RCntxt::hasSourceRefs() const\n    return refs && TYPEOF(refs) != NILSXP;\n }\n \n+SEXP RCntxt::contextSourceRefs() const\n+{\n+   // retrieve the source reference tagged on the context\n+   SEXP ref = srcref();\n+   \n+   // if this is a byte-code context, we need to do some\n+   // extra work to resolve the \"real\" source reference (if any)\n+   if (isByteCodeSrcRef(ref))\n+   {\n+      r::sexp::Protect protect;\n+   \n+      // stuff context parameters into a list to avoid accidentally\n+      // evaluating call objects prematurely\n+      r::sexp::ListBuilder builder(&protect);\n+      builder.add(\"call\", call());\n+      builder.add(\"callflag\", callflag());\n+      builder.add(\"callfun\", callfun());\n+      builder.add(\"srcref\", srcref());\n+      builder.add(\"cloenv\", cloenv());\n+      SEXP info = r::sexp::create(builder, &protect);", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "ac1b6575cdd71e4c6e98a8feaebf632669ef5daf"}, "originalPosition": 23}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMTM3Mjk3NQ==", "bodyText": "We should add a comment here indicating the difference between contextSourceRefs and sourceRefs", "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/pull/8002#discussion_r501372975", "createdAt": "2020-10-07T23:49:13Z", "author": {"login": "jmcphers"}, "path": "src/cpp/r/include/r/RCntxt.hpp", "diffHunk": "@@ -63,6 +63,7 @@ class RCntxt: public RCntxtInterface\n    bool isDebugHidden() const;\n    bool isErrorHandler() const;\n \n+   SEXP contextSourceRefs() const;", "state": "SUBMITTED", "replyTo": null, "originalCommit": {"oid": "ac1b6575cdd71e4c6e98a8feaebf632669ef5daf"}, "originalPosition": 4}]}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "6d15982992c0ed495fb7b36064faee4a6158c70e", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/6d15982992c0ed495fb7b36064faee4a6158c70e", "committedDate": "2020-10-08T16:27:58Z", "message": "add helper for dumping contexts"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "cd8e77667f45f3d044c3cb4991158f6d6417baa5", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/cd8e77667f45f3d044c3cb4991158f6d6417baa5", "committedDate": "2020-10-08T16:27:58Z", "message": "resolve srcrefs for bytecode contexts"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "e7657b90dcc367a3be88e14da0cf46e957e72441", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/e7657b90dcc367a3be88e14da0cf46e957e72441", "committedDate": "2020-10-08T16:27:58Z", "message": "formatting"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "9f93a5e2f03adf55f46c8f89e3e75cbd1bde66d7", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/9f93a5e2f03adf55f46c8f89e3e75cbd1bde66d7", "committedDate": "2020-10-08T16:27:58Z", "message": "avoid repeated calls to contextSourceRefs()"}}, {"__typename": "HeadRefForcePushedEvent", "beforeCommit": {"oid": "ac1b6575cdd71e4c6e98a8feaebf632669ef5daf", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/ac1b6575cdd71e4c6e98a8feaebf632669ef5daf", "committedDate": "2020-10-07T22:20:32Z", "message": "avoid repeated calls to contextSourceRefs()"}, "afterCommit": {"oid": "9f93a5e2f03adf55f46c8f89e3e75cbd1bde66d7", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/9f93a5e2f03adf55f46c8f89e3e75cbd1bde66d7", "committedDate": "2020-10-08T16:27:58Z", "message": "avoid repeated calls to contextSourceRefs()"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "e1a4eaf20e557d62f465e0c9e05847ab2bcf17d1", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/e1a4eaf20e557d62f465e0c9e05847ab2bcf17d1", "committedDate": "2020-10-08T16:51:10Z", "message": "clarify distinction between context, callfun srcref"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "d2a3dcc2681caaea1863956574e0142020617c7a", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/d2a3dcc2681caaea1863956574e0142020617c7a", "committedDate": "2020-10-08T16:52:19Z", "message": "exact = TRUE"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "9777e4dddb76e95af01c676b79d8625f07bb4721", "author": {"user": {"login": "kevinushey", "name": "Kevin Ushey"}}, "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/commit/9777e4dddb76e95af01c676b79d8625f07bb4721", "committedDate": "2020-10-08T16:54:20Z", "message": "missed rename"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestReview", "id": "MDE3OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3NTA1OTA4NzI4", "url": "https://github.com/rstudio/rstudio/pull/8002#pullrequestreview-505908728", "createdAt": "20